# Dev-checkout artifacts under src/hermes/mcp/<name>/. Never needed in a
# build context: the router only reads templates via a runtime volume mount
# (never bakes them in — see Dockerfile's scoped COPY), and Dockerfile.hermes
# generates its own shared /opt/node_modules from src/hermes/mcp/package.json
# rather than copying any template's local node_modules.
